{"tid":798073,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國房產》深圳新地產項目設租金管制，租金年漲幅不可超過５％","createTime":"2018-08-29T04:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T17:03:36.000Z","uid":13663,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4281700bb89441c8bd06cf7373ac351fade798bc","tid":798073,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:34:16.000Z","msg":"《中國房產》深圳新地產項目設租金管制，租金年漲幅不可超過５％<br />\n以更佳效果檢視 &raquo;<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社２９日專訊》據內媒報道，深圳正在探索建立全市穩租金商品房項目制度，首先在深圳地鐵和深業集團合資開發的塘朗城精品公寓為試點項目，採取嚴格的租金管制，一房一價、一年一調，租金年增長率最高不超過５％，並且只面向深圳繳納社保滿一年的未購房居民，申請人在網上申請後進入排隊程序。該項目為高區２４８套房、無縫接駁地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b768aea99c7e6782897cc289fb3dedf34a6c94d5","tid":798073,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:34:33.000Z","msg":"又然"},{"pid":"a876a494a3dca9523e96ea597336dc434dcd04df","tid":798073,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"幾時到香港"},{"pid":"00b9f63fa648b102736f94c90c50a5f841ff440b","tid":798073,"uid":190540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ff9cbcdcd896c5d46b3748322bc13fff90b2ab9","tid":798073,"uid":745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"4.99999%"},{"pid":"efce5f4655444cefe9802ab965f85f8462e910e2","tid":798073,"uid":182475,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"限購、限售、限租，呢個係咩樓市? 有入無出，賣緊來來曱甴屋?"},{"pid":"05d2d887bd27cdb203c56482b76a1b9a8ed2dfac","tid":798073,"uid":62935,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"好癲<br />\n<br />\n隨時林鄭施政報告前又被人召一召上去<br />\n番黎出多幾招"},{"pid":"8ed9c1c63aa0d35f492f7cd1e86b700b9553baed","tid":798073,"uid":31907,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"為左消除二手市場"},{"pid":"1346aff45517bd20d75d3b30c5af7